and]], Australia. |{{coord|24|47|S|155|48|E|name=USS William H. Standley (CG-32)}} |- |[[USS Elliot (DD-967)|USS ''Elliot'']] |22 June 2005 |A [[Spruance-class destroyer|''Spruance''-class]] [[destroyer]] that was sunk as a target 100 nautical miles east of [[Fraser Island]], Australia. |{{coord|24|43|S|155|50|E|name=USS Elliot (DD-967)}} |}
